'''Proceduralist''' is a [[physician]], usually a specialist or [[subspecialist]] who performs different diagnostic or therapeutic procedures.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.managedcaremag.com/archives/2007/10/proceduralists-seem-task|title=Proceduralists Seem Up To the Task|date=1 October 2007|website=Managedcaremag.com|accessdate=26 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-hospitalist.org/hospitalist/article/123570/those-who-do|title=Those Who Do|website=The-hospitalist.org|accessdate=26 November 2017}}</ref>

